You should make sure the tkinter Python module is installed.
This module is not installed through pip.

Windows
=======
When you install Python using the official installer,
make sure to check the option to install Tcl/Tk with IDLE.

macOS (https://brew.sh/)
========================
brew install python-tk@3.10
(or whatever Python version you have)

Alternatively install the offical binaries: https://www.python.org/downloads/
As with Windows, they should come with Tcl/Tk.

Ubuntu/Debian
=============
sudo apt-get install python3-tk
or
sudo apt-get install python3.10-tk
(or whatever Python version you have)

Fedora
======
sudo dnf install python3-tkinter

CentOS
======
sudo yum install python3-tkinter